A stupidly simple Django model introspection API.

A blog post explaining it's usage:

http://ericholscher.com/blog/2010/feb/14/django-inspect-generic-introspection-api-django-mo/

Latest Test Results:

http://devmason.com/pony_server/django_inspect

Check out the tests for usage.

